Approval Validator Command Line Tool
----------------------------------------------------

Pre-requisites:
	python-2.7 and above

To run the tool
   $python validate_approvals.py --approvers [args] --changed-files [args]   

To run the testcases
	$ ./testcases.sh testcases.txt

If tool returns error due to missing library, run
   $sudo pip install <library_name>

If pip is not present, run
   $sudo easy_install pip